00:16:47.798 --> 00:16:48.966
¿Dormiste un poco?

00:16:50.592 --> 00:16:51.885
Toma algo de fruta.

00:16:54.096 --> 00:16:55.139
Se-mi.

00:16:55.806 --> 00:16:56.640
Sí.

00:16:57.391 --> 00:16:59.226
Estás cerca de Hwi-gyeong, ¿verdad?

00:17:01.687 --> 00:17:03.814
